{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_06_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 始まりに過ぎませんから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ？\n出版社側に、違う構図を提案したい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nYou want to propose a different composition to the publisher?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.0072563808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことでしょう\nさっきの私の仕事に、何か不備でもありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?\nWas there something wrong with my work earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.0322680473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳ではないんですが……俺は、出来れば\nアイドルには素の表情を見せてほしいと思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not it‚ but… If possible‚\nI’d like idols to show their natural expressions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのカメラテストも、とても良かったですけど\n本当のmihoさんとはやっぱり違うなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The camera test earlier went really well too‚\nbut it felt different from the real Miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8649967946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9842855136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの、素の表情？　……そんなの表に出した途端\n星見プロの信頼も全て失うことになると思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's natural expression? …If we reveal that‚\nI think Hoshimi Production will lose all trust.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2392964681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "自分でそれを言いますか……\nま……まぁ、出来る範囲ということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re saying that yourself…\nW-Well‚ I meant within reason…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さんが考える\n私の素顔というのは、どんなろくでもないものですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what kind of ridiculous expression\nDo you think is my “true expression‚” {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.265192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきの、ため息をついてた顔\nあっちの方がずっと、mihoさんらしいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Your face when you were sighing earlier.\nI think that's more like the real miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0389338175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……喧嘩を売るつもりもなく、そういうことを言う\n度胸だけは大したものだと思いますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To say such things without intending to pick a fightー\nyour nerve alone is quite something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6475278536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……ウエディングドレスでため息をつくような\n状況を考えて、向こうに提案したいということですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… you want to propose a situation to them\nwhere I’m sighing in a wedding dress?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。そういうことです\nもちろんmihoさんが嫌でなければですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes‚ that’s what I meant.\nOf course‚ only if you’re okay with it‚ miho-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1766431807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……ウエディングドレスを着る時は\n未来の話をしていると、貴方がさっき言ったんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… You said that people talk about the future\nwhen they wear wedding dresses‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "ましてや、ブライダル情報誌で\nそんなもの、通る訳がないと思いますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ in a bridal magazine‚\nI don't think such a thing would ever pass.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.9926069259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、マリッジブルーがどうこうって\n前にmihoさんが話してたでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ you were talking about\nwedding blues and such before‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "結婚するけど、ちょっと不安もある花嫁さんという\n構図なら、mihoさんにも合うんじゃないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought a composition of a bride who’s happy to get married\nbut also a little anxious might suit you‚ Miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7659853617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……雑誌の内容やテキスト次第ですけど\nそのくらいなら、なんとかなるかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… it depends on the magazine's content and text‚\nbut something like that might work out somehow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "通るかはともかく、話してみる分には構わないのでは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Regardless of whether it passes‚ there's no harm in discussing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6115863164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9887970448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9887970448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8683888991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……辛気くさいと、あの二人には散々言われますけど\nこの顔なりに、使い道というのはあるものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Those two always tell me I’m gloomy‚\nbut I guess even my face has its uses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6736772969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それを考えるのが、マネージャーの俺の仕事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about that is my job as a manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6551916043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.4998172362
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.4998172362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（俺の提案は、出版社の担当者をだいぶ困らせたものの）\n（別にページを取って、載せてもらえることになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My proposal quite troubled the publisher's representative‚ but）\n（they decided to give it a separate page and include it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.724533836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それでは本番、お願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's begin the actual shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.724533836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "結婚はゴールではなくて\n新たな生活の始まりに過ぎませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Marriage isn’t the goal—\nit's just the beginning of a new life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "期待と同じくらい、不安だってあると思うんです\n今までの生活との別れの時でもある訳で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think there’s just as much anxiety as there is anticipation.\nIt's also a time of farewell to your previous life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2666575114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "結婚してからのトラブルなんて\n実際、いくらでもあるでしょうしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And in reality‚ there are plenty of\ntroubles that come up after marriage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.399110455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
