      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、不安なだけでは、救いがないですし\nそこから立ち上がるところまで、表現出来たらと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it’s no good if it’s all just anxiety‚\nso I’d like to be able to show someone rising above that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.5333007811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
