      "text": "（うん、やっぱり凄くいい表情だ。結婚とは違うけど）\n（……mihoさんも、辛い別れを経験した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yeah‚ her expression is really good. It’s not about marriage though.）\n（…miho-san has experienced a painful separation too.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9333038328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、その悲しみを振り切って再び立ち上がって）\n（新たなグループの一員として、今ここに立ってる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yet‚ she overcame that sadness and rose again‚）\n（and now stands here as a member of a new group.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.3666341143,
